    {
      "color": "3",
      "height": 380,
      "id": "seat-enums",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "## Enumerations\n\n### SeatStatus\n- AVAILABLE (예약 가능)\n- RESERVED (예약 완료)\n\n### OccupancyStatus\n- ACTIVE (활성)\n- EXPIRED (만료)\n- CONFIRMED (확정)\n\n### SeatGrade\n- VIP / R / S / A\n\n### SeatCategory\n- NORMAL (일반석)\n- COUPLE (커플석)",
      "type": "text",
