      "id": "show",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "## Show\n**Aggregate Root**\n\n### 속성\n- id: Long\n- title: String\n- description: String\n- pricePolicy: PricePolicy\n- performances: List<Performance>\n\n### 메서드\n+ addPerformance(Performance): void\n+ getPriceFor(SeatGrade): int\n\n### 역할\n공연 작품 전체 관리\n(예: 레미제라블)",
      "type": "text",
