      "id": "price-policy",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "## PricePolicy\n**Value Object**\n\n### 속성\n- vipPrice: int\n- rPrice: int\n- sPrice: int\n- aPrice: int\n\n### 메서드\n+ getPriceFor(SeatGrade): int\n\n### 특징\n불변 객체",
      "type": "text",
