      "id": "seat-occupancy",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "## SeatOccupancy\n**Aggregate Root** ⭐\n\n### 속성\n- id: Long\n- seat: Seat\n- userId: Long\n- performance: Performance\n- period: OccupancyPeriod\n- status: OccupancyStatus\n\n### 메서드\n+ isActive(): boolean\n+ expire(): void\n+ confirm(): void\n+ occupy(): void 🔔\n\n### 역할\n5분간 좌석 임시 점유",
