      },
      "text": "## OccupancyPeriod\n**Value Object**\n\n### 속성\n- startedAt: LocalDateTime\n- expiresAt: LocalDateTime\n\n### 메서드\n+ ofMinutes(int): OccupancyPeriod\n+ isExpired(): boolean\n+ getRemainingTime(): Duration\n\n### 특징\n5분 타이머",
      "type": "text",
