      "y": -750
    },
    {
      "color": "3",
      "height": 380,
      "id": "seat",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "## Seat\n**Aggregate Root**\n\n### 속성\n- id: Long\n- performance: Performance\n- position: SeatPosition\n- status: SeatStatus\n\n### 메서드\n+ isAvailable(): boolean\n+ reserve(): void\n+ release(): void\n+ getGrade(): SeatGrade\n+ getCategory(): SeatCategory\n+ getPrice(Show): int\n\n### 역할\n좌석의 물리적 정보와 상태",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 380,
      "x": -1550,
      "y": 100
    },
    {
      "color": "3",
      "height": 380,
      "id": "seat-position",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "## SeatPosition\n**Value Object** ⭐\n\n### 속성\n- row: int [1-20]\n- column: int [1-20]\n\n### 메서드\n+ getGrade(): SeatGrade\n+ getCategory(): SeatCategory\n+ isCoupleArea(): boolean\n+ getPairPosition(): SeatPosition\n+ isSameRow(SeatPosition): boolean\n\n### 규칙\n- 행 1-3: VIP\n- 행 4-8: R\n- 행 9-14: S\n- 행 15-20: A\n- 열 1-18: 일반석\n- 열 19-20: 커플석",
